file.name: TraceResponse.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
TraceResponse:
  type: object
  description: |
    The object containing all trace data for the request, only present if the trace token was provided in the request.
  additionalProperties:
    type: object
    properties:
      traceKey:
        type: string
      traceValue:
        type: object
